job_description:
For our client, HQ based in Monaco, we are recruiting a Consolidation Specialist. Our client is an investment company with a diverse portfolio of internationally active companies. In this role you will responsible for the consolidation and management reporting. Are you adventures and ready to move to Monoca? After a few years abroad you will be working in the Rotterdam office (the Netherlands). Please continue to read!
Your potential employer

This investment company has a rich history and for this they are worldwide known. The strategy is to focus on acquiring significant shareholdings in companies, with the objective of increasing long-term shareholder value. They only invest in companies with a strong and sustainable market position and good long-term perspectives in which there is the opportunity to grow the business, either through acquisitions (buy & build) or organic growth.

With a group of 60 people they work closely together with the management teams of the companies to support them in executing their strategic plans.

Your tasks and responsibilities

The Finance team is stationed in Monaco and excists of 4 people. You will be responsible to consolidate the whole portfolio to the mangement. You will work together closely with another consolidation specialist and he will also be the one that will learn you all the ins and outs. After a few years in Monaco you will be stationed in the Rotterdam office, the Netherlands.

Maintaining and improving the SAP (BO) Financial Consolidation environment and underlying data model;
Initial analysis of reporting sets from portfolio companies;
First point of contact for portfolio companies on periodic reporting;
Preparation of the consolidation in SAP;
Preparation of management reporting.

Your experience and knowledge
Completed bachelor in finance and/or information studies;
Minimum 5 year relevant working experience in consolidation;
Good comprehension of the English language (verbal and in writing), knowledge of the Dutch language is a plus;
Experience with SAP financial consolidation is a plus.

Your competencies and unique talents

Able to work both independently and in an international team;
Natural tendency to take responsibility;
Looking for room to improve, driving the change;
Based out of Monaco and open to (limited) travel within Europe.

Interested? Please apply and I will respond to your application as soon as possible.

